My interpretation of this song is 
While I was watching the trees wind bowing through then I realised 
How they keep on standing they move with the wind but they don't change their shape their essence in thr nature , that's exactly what this song makes me feel like that no matter one has to keep on standing true to its roots 
Under teray raaz kahi haine , khud se mil payga oh Yaara dil se jo sun paye ga 
Na chor allah ka wada na bhool just keep standing keep fighting keep at it 

Because Allah is there
